{"tid":608914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再接再厲，支那正趕製載人太空站，2022年將投入營運！！","createTime":"2018-03-28T14:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T17:23:49.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f52908d2e824ec846497834c5a3f717f1a9df10b","tid":608914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"中國進入太空第一人、載人航太工程辦公室副主任楊利偉接受《解放軍報》專訪時表示，支那載人太空站2022年前後將投入營運。<br />\n<br />\n楊利偉指出，支那載人航太工程第三步任務&mdash;太空站工程已全面展開。載人太空站計畫到2022年前後完成並投入營運，展開較大規模的太空科學實驗與技術試驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，支那太空站基本構型包括核心艙和兩個實驗艙，採用對稱T形構型，軌道傾角42度，高度340至450公里，設計壽命10年，額定成員3人，乘組輪換時最多可達6人，乘組一般在軌執行任務週期為半年，而太空站各艙段將由長征五號B運載火箭，在文昌航太發射場發射；貨運飛船將由長征七號運載火箭發射；神舟載人飛船將由長征二號F火箭在酒泉衛星發射中心發射。<br />\n<br />\n另外他還提到今年是支那載人航太工程第三步任務的關鍵之年。為太空站任務改進研製的長征五號B運載火箭，將於3月轉入試樣階段，後續將開展發射場合練及首飛任務前的準備工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。太空站核心艙將完成設備齊套及艙體總裝，相關大型地面聯合試驗逐步展開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3023387?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3023387%3Ffrom%3Dudn-referralnews_ch2artbottom&d=rjVGkcL2WRkkAMqrJz%2F5yv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4daa5542\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3023387?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom</a>"},{"pid":"8316bb7667077efef304d7bc2c4afaa4289ce970","tid":608914,"uid":99205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"玩完一次仲唔夠皮咩<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69777f202ef5e5ba9623f7789fe2713c577fac62","tid":608914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"楊利偉透露，支那將於明年6月前後實施長征五號B運載火箭的首飛任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後陸續發射太空站核心艙和實驗艙，進行太空站的在軌組裝建造。"},{"pid":"9051eaafbeab46744113f0ed543279811a440d44","tid":608914,"uid":511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"嫌跌唔撚夠多嘢落嚟呀，屌你老母臭支西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9762e63d7d04a4965712124d1c21983bf569ad","tid":608914,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"睇嚟就快有宇宙通行證"},{"pid":"43ebcee0b560be109370390a4b2832ba9f2983e6","tid":608914,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ba2b7dcbaa1856a9d6f76052f125feae7d073b5","tid":608914,"uid":81113,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"43ebcee0b560be109370390a4b2832ba9f2983e6","tid":608914,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"咁勁，又唔見你個刁總上太空？"},{"pid":"87bd86ff0bfc85fbd8ad9e68b9ca1da3ec087011","tid":608914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43ebcee0b560be109370390a4b2832ba9f2983e6","tid":608914,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"7c567c40740a9ed87d7334de4850ca3f7ac73c80","tid":608914,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f19f1523f4d11d1e77fcbcd11eb74fd0fc0a865","tid":608914,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7c567c40740a9ed87d7334de4850ca3f7ac73c80","tid":608914,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"87bd86ff0bfc85fbd8ad9e68b9ca1da3ec087011","tid":608914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43ebcee0b560be109370390a4b2832ba9f2983